text: Calochone is a genus of flowering plants in the family Rubiaceae. The genus is found in Cameroon, Gabon, Cabinda Province, Republic of the Congo, and Democratic Republic of the Congo. ==Species== * Calochone acuminata Keay \- Cabinda, Cameroon, Gabon * Calochone redingii (De Wild.)
